[01:05.45]There are no inhabitants of this land of despair. A band of Pawnees（波尼族） or of Blackfeet（黑脚族） may occasionally traverse（横穿） it in order to reach other hunting-grounds, but the hardiest of the braves are glad to lose sight of those awesome plains, and to find themselves once more upon their prairies. 
