[01:48.11]In the whole world there can be no more dreary（沉闷的） view than that from the northern slope of the Sierra Blanco（布兰卡山脉）. As far as the eye can reach stretches the great flat plain- land, all dusted over with patches of alkali, and intersected by clumps of the dwarfish chaparral bushes. 
