[02:25.53]There is no bird in the steel-blue heaven, no movement upon the dull, grey earth—above all, there is absolute silence. Listen as one may, there is no shadow of a sound in all that mighty wilderness（荒野）; nothing but silence—complete and heart-subduing silence. 
